Softwares Required: Java 8 or above, Appachi tomcate server
Connect tomcat to Eclips : to easily deploy applications to tomcate

IoC : the approach of outsourcing the construction and management of object. that outsourcing will be hundeled
by an ojbect factory. (application context ...)
- to make our application configurable : so that our dependcies should work with any type of implementation 
with our touching the source code. (using interface), loose coupling
Java classes are called POJOs
